    <item>
      <title>巴拉圭着眼于下半年进一步实现债务去美元化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/paraguay-eyes-window-to-further-de-dollarize-debt-in-second-half</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴拉圭财政部长卡洛斯·费尔南德斯表示，如果能够以优惠的利率进行的话，巴拉圭可能会在今年下半年将部分美元债务换成期限较长的本币债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/paraguay-eyes-window-to-further-de-dollarize-debt-in-second-half</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 21:03:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥夫拉多尔扩大了墨西哥的军事力量。它建造机场而不是遏制谋杀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-18/mexico-president-amlo-traded-security-for-infrastructure-during-his-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[洛佩兹·奥夫拉多尔责成武装部队建设基础设施和确保公共安全。他的任期结束时将新建交通枢纽、酒店和博物馆 —以及超过 170,000 起谋杀案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-18/mexico-president-amlo-traded-security-for-infrastructure-during-his-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 21:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
